## 6. Project conventions

- **Script style**: `<script setup lang="ts">` with TypeScript everywhere (Vue 3.5 SFCs). `vue-tsc` used in build.
- **UI library**: **No component UI library** (no Element Plus, no Headless UI in deps). UI is **custom Tailwind CSS** (`tailwindcss` + `tailwindcss-animate`, `tailwind-merge`, `clsx`). Icons via **`lucide-vue-next`** + emoji. Drag-and-drop via **`vue-draggable-plus`**. Charts via `chart.js`. Diagrams via `d3`/`mermaid`.
- **Confirmations**: **`sweetalert2`** (`Swal.fire({...})`) for all confirm/number-input/password prompts (transfer, merge, split-order count, cancel PIN).
- **Modals/dialogs pattern**: custom inline `<Transition name="fade">` wrappers — outer `fixed inset-0 z-[10000] flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-xs`, inner `bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-{lg|md}` with a gradient header (`bg-gradient-to-r from-{color}-500 to-{color}-600 text-white px-6 py-4`), body, and `bg-gray-50 px-6 py-4 flex justify-end gap-3 border-t` footer with Cancel + primary action. The only reusable modal component is `src/components/reception/ManagerAuthModal.vue` (props `actionType`, `targetName`; emits `confirm`, `close`).
- **State management**: **Pinia** (`pinia` ^3). Stores in `src/stores/` (e.g. `useRestaurantStore`, `useLanguageStore`). Accessed via `useXxxStore()` + `storeToRefs`.
- **Composables**: in `src/composables/`, all **`.ts`** files, exported as `export function useXxx()`. Pattern: return refs + async functions; use `@/lib/supabase` client + RPC functions (`hall_*`).
- **Components**: in `src/components/{domain}/` (e.g. `reception/`, `customer/`, `requisition/`, `loyalty/`).
- **Data service pattern**: **Supabase client** (`@supabase/supabase-js` ^2) via `src/lib/supabase.ts`, called through **RPC functions** (e.g. `hall_list_tables`, `hall_get_checkout_totals`, `hall_cancel_order_or_item`) parameterized by `p_branch_id` from `useBranch()` (`activeBranchId` / `throwBranchGuard`). Mock fallback exists: tables with ids starting with `mock-` skip the Supabase calls (see `executeCancel`). Menu data is static from `src/data/menuData.ts`. **Important caveat**: the table transfer/merge/split execute functions currently mutate only local Pinia state and do NOT call any Supabase RPC — so there is no server-side persistence/atomicity for those operations yet.
- **i18n**: `vue-i18n` ^9 via `useLanguageStore().t`; locales in `src/locales/{vi,en,ja}.ts`. Relevant keys: `reception.select_split_items` ("Chọn món cần tách sang phiếu mới"), `reception.click_highlighted_table`, `reception.cancel_esc`, `reception.source`, `reception.select`, `layout.operations` ("Nghiệp vụ").
- **Types**: `src/types/database.ts` (e.g. `Zone`, `TableT`, `TableStatus`).

